Package: lifetime
Type: Package
Title: Provide functions for lifetime pricing
Version: 1.0
Authors@R: person("Dan", "Kary", email = "dan@southwickassociates.com", role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: This packages was based on the NC project from late 2019, including
